These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-1::.
4 different games are played: backgammon, scrabble, chess, domino
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, car, motorbike, roller
1. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing backgammon is on the right of the person playing domino##1
3. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person playing chess is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the car and the person driving the motorbike##2
6. the person playing domino is the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |    4     |
| Game   | domino | backgammon     | chess | scrabble |
| Transport     | bike     | motorbike | roller  | car      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-2::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, soccer, water-polo, lacrosse
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, helicopter, snowmobile, trike
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the far right##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |   4   |
| Sport   | badminton | soccer    | lacrosse     | water-polo  |
| Transport     | bus    | snowmobile | helicopter | trike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-3::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: house, jazz, pop, rock
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, poppy, balloon-flower, marigold
1. the person who growsmarigold is on the left or right of the fan of jazz##3
2. the fan of jazz is on the far left##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan of rock##1
4. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the fan of house##3
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the right of the fan of pop##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |   3    |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | pop   | house  | rock |
| Flower           | poppy | marigold | balloon-flower | orchid  |

