.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-4::.
4 different games are played: chess, poker, backgammon, go
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, brazilian, egyptian, indian
1. the indian is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
2. the person playing go is between the person playing chess and the egyptian##2
3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person playing backgammon##3
4. the egyptian is on the left or right of the indian##3
5. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing poker##1
6. the argentine is on the right of the brazilian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |    4     |
| Game         | poker | chess | go | backgammon  |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | argentine   | indian  | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-5::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, banana, lettuce, potato
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, hiking, singing, woodworking
1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lettuce is on the right of the person eating banana##1
3. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person eating potato##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |    2    |       3       |      4      |
| Food   | pomegranate    | banana   | lettuce | potato    |
| Hobby      | hiking | drawing | singing       | woodworking |

