.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-6::.
City: hamburg, miami, liverpool, nizza
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, roller, train, tram
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
2. the person driving the train is between the person driving the tram and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the person driving the boat is between the person driving the train and the person traveling to hamburg##2
4. the person driving the tram is on the far right##1
5. the person traveling to miami is on the left or right of the person traveling to nizza##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2   |    3     |   4   |
| City    | hamburg | liverpool | nizza | miami |
| Transport   | roller | boat  | train    | tram  |

