.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-7::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, classical, blues, techno
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, ship, snowmobile, van
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the fan of country is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person driving the ship is on the left of the person driving the snowmobile##1
4. the fan of blues is between the fan of classical and the fan of techno##2
5. the person driving the ship is the person driving the ship##1
6. the person driving the ship is between the person driving the snowmobile and the fan of techno##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |  2   |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | country | techno | blues | classical     |
| Transport     | airplane | van  | ship   | snowmobile |

