.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-9::.
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, horse, snake
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, scooter, snowmobile, van
1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person driving the trike##1
2. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the van is the owner of the snake##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far left or far right##3
6. the owner of the fish is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the trike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish   | horse      | snake      |
| Transport   | scooter     | snowmobile | trike | van |

