.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, jazz, salsa
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skateboarding, rugby, weightlifting, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the fan of jazz is between the person who's sport is volleyball and the person who's sport is rugby##2
3. the fan of electronic is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the left or right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3     |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | classical | electronic | jazz      | salsa   |
| Sport   | weightlifting  | rugby    | skateboarding | volleyball |

