.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, chess, hiking, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, epic, disaster, romance
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |   2    |      3      |   4    |
| Hobby   | baking     | chess  | woodworking | hiking |
| Movie-Genre     | thriller | romance | epic     | disaster    |

