.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-13::.
There are 4 different nationalities: american, canadian, german, turkish
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, chaman, havana, blend
1. the canadian is on the far right##1
2. the american is the american##1
3. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the tiparillo-smoker##3
4. the tiparillo-smoker is on the left or right of the canadian##3
5. the german is on the left or right of the turkish##3
6. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the turkish##3
7. the tiparillo-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Nationality   | american | german  | turkish | canadian |
| Cigar           | havana     | blend | tiparillo    | chaman     |

