3. the person playing go is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rugby##3
4. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Game   | go | canasta | snooker | backgammon |
| Sport         | parkour  | rugby   | soccer | golf     |

