.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-17::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, yellow, apricot, azure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, dubstep, indie, punk
1. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
2. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who likes azure##1
3. the person who likes ivory is on the left or right of the fan of dubstep##3
4. the fan of dubstep is on the right of the fan of disco##1
5. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who likes yellow##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |   3   |   4   |
| Color      | ivory | yellow    | azure  | apricot |
| Music-Genre   | disco       | dubstep | indie | punk  |

