.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-3-20::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, fanta, milk, soy-milk
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, baking, cooking, hiking
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
4. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person drinking cola##1
7. the person drinking milk is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is cooking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |    2     |       3       |    4     |
| Beverage   | fanta     | cola     | milk          | soy-milk |
| Hobby      | board-games | baking | hiking | cooking  |

 